			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">All your transactions are secure when you place an order online at Nexthealth.pk. Your personal information is encrypted by using Let's Encrypt SSL (Secure Sockets Layer) Certificate with encryption 256-bit technology before being sent over the Internet, which ensures the privacy and high level of security of all your information.</span></td>
