				</span></td>
			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">By using this Website, it is deemed that you have consented to receive all communications from Nexthealth.pk or by Service Providers on our behalf including but not limited to calls, SMS’s, auto-dialed and/or pre-recorded messages at any time subject to the Privacy Policy for the purposes of clarifications, marketing and promotions. In case you wish to stop the contact with us for the same, you may send us an email to the effect at our designation email address on our Website.</span></td>
