				<span style=" ">The website allows you to place your orders after your registration by following the ordering process provided on the Website. If a product or medicine requires prescription, you are required to provide your prescription to enable you to complete your order. A prescription is mandatory for all Narcotics and Controlled Substances which includes all prescription medicines as defined by the Ministry of Health, Government of Pakistan. Shipment of the order will not be carried out until we receive a prescription from a qualified healthcare professional.</span></td>
