		<tr>
			<td style="width: 6.5268%; vertical-align: top;">
				<span style=" ">4.2</span></td>
			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">Nexthealth.pk is a fully licensed and regulated pharmacy and takes all precautions to strictly abide by the laws and regulations set forth in the dispensing of prescription medications. By placing the order for your prescription medicines, you acknowledge and accept the following terms regarding the purchase of any prescription medicines.</span></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
