		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td style="width: 6.5268%; vertical-align: top;">
				<span style=" ">4.6</span></td>
			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">The drug information provided in the Nexthealth.pk is for informative purposes only and this Website is not intended to provide diagnosis, treatment or medical advice. We are not liable for any adverse effects or harm to you as a result of your reliance on the information on the Website.</span></td>
		</tr>
