			<td style="width: 6.5268%; vertical-align: top;">
				<span style=" ">4.7</span></td>
			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">Nexthealth.pk requires either the User or Customer or qualified healthcare professional to confirm that he/she is completely aware of the indications, side effects, drug interactions and effects of missed dose or overdose of the medicines he/she orders from us. It is imperative to seek professional advice from your physician before purchasing or consuming any medicine from Nexthealth.pk.</span></td>
