				<span style=" ">5.11</span></td>
			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">You understand that all Products shall be sold and dispensed by a registered Pharmacist at Nexthealth.pk and/or its affiliates.</span></td>
