		<tr>
			<td style="width: 6.5268%; vertical-align: top;">
				<span style=" ">5.12</span></td>
			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">If you are the patient/parent/authorized person on behalf of the patient, you authorize and appoint the Nexthealth.pk and/or its affiliates, as your attorney and agent, to take all steps, sign all documents and to act on your behalf as if you were personally present and acting for yourself for the limited purposes of (i) obtaining a valid prescription for any prescription which you have sent to us; (ii) packaging your prescriptions and delivering them to you; and (iii) take all ancillary steps related to your desired transaction. By making any purchase, you hereby authorize Nexthealth.pk and/or its affiliates to ship the order by courier to your designated location. This authorization shall include, but not be limited to collecting and using your personal and personal health information as reasonably necessary for the fulfillment of your order. "You have read and understand these terms and agree that they shall be binding upon you and your assigns, heirs and personal representatives." If you are the parent/legal guardian/authorized person for the patient disclosed herein, “you affirm that you are over the age of majority, and have full authority to sign for and provide the above representations to the Nexthealth.pk and/or its affiliates on the Patient's behalf."</span></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td style="width: 6.5268%; vertical-align: top;">
