		<tr>
			<td style="width: 6.5268%; vertical-align: top;">
				<span style=" ">6.1</span></td>
			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">You cannot edit or change your order once you have completed the process of placing an order and the order ID is generated. But you can cancel your order at any time before the payment is processed. Once you have made the payment, you are liable to pay 15% restocking fee and the remaining amount would be credited back through banking channel. We do not entertain cash refunds.</span></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td style="width: 6.5268%; vertical-align: top;">
				<span style=" ">6.2</span></td>
			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">We do our best to ensure that the products you order are delivered according to your specifications. However, should you receive an incomplete, damaged or incorrect Product(s), CONTACT US within 24 hours of receiving the Product(s). We will not accept liability for such delivery issues, if you fail to notify us within 24 hours of receipt of the Product(s).</span></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td style="width: 6.5268%; vertical-align: top;">
				<span style=" ">6.3</span></td>
			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">A full refund is possible on the return of a Product if (i) the delivered Product is lost or damaged from outside during transit; or (ii) Defective; or (iii) Expired. If the package is damaged on the outside, do not accept the package and do not sign the delivery slip. Simply return the damaged package. Signing of the delivery slip is taken as your consent that the package has not been damaged in transit. &nbsp;</span></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td style="width: 6.5268%; vertical-align: top;">
				<span style=" ">6.4</span></td>
			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">We also understand that various circumstances may arise leading you to want to return, replace or exchange a Product(s) that is not defective. In these cases, we may allow the return of unopened, unused products after deducting a 15% restocking charge, only if you notify us within 10 working days of receipt subject to exceptions listed herein below.</span></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td style="width: 6.5268%; vertical-align: top;">
				<span style=" ">6.5</span></td>
			<td style="width: 93.3566%; text-align: justify;">
				<span style=" ">Cold chain Product(s) and certain Product(s) marked on the Website marked with the precaution “Not returnable for refund or exchange" are not eligible for return, replacement, exchange or refund. &nbsp;</span></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td style="width: 6.5268%; vertical-align: top;">
